        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Exegetically",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", the unconditional submission here required cannot to any extent be toned down by means of limitations mentally supplied (in opposition to Michaelis, Storr, Kuinoel, and others). The ethical relations already subsisting in each particular case determine what limitations must actually be made. Comp. the remark after ",
        "children": []
